      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey my 4 year old is running a really high fever and won't stop coughing. he's about 16kg. i have some infant/children's acetaminophen liquid (the 160mg per 5mL kind). how much should i give him right now to get the fever down? i dont want to give too little so it doesnt work",
